reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect travel cubes
reviews.reviewText: We used these to pack clothes in on a road trip to bring into the hotel and it was perfect for the clothes for each day. Lasted 2 years I bought more for our next trip.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These cubes work amazingly well!
reviews.reviewText: I ordered two sets of these cubes in extra large. I was amazed with how much each one held. I could have fit the 4 into large suitcase but only needed 3. Once at our destination, it was much easier to unpack and stow our clothes. I will be ordering small sizes but I highly recommend them!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 27, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good value for the price but not super durable
reviews.reviewText: I bought these to use in our RV for packing clothes for each family member. They are large enough for a couple days worth of clothes. Great for a weekend trip. The quality is not the best. One of the zippers is already separating but I was able to fix it. These were a little less expensive than other brands so you get what you pay for. Good enough for occasional use.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best thing ever!
reviews.reviewText: I bought these for our cruise because there is not alot of storage on the ship. I loved how I was able to organize all of my clothes. They fit perfectly in my suitcase and then easily into the storage space I had in the room. My clothes stayed organized my entire trip.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for packing
reviews.reviewText: I do not know how I lived without these all these years. I am going on a 12 day vacation and these helped me fit everything in my suitcase. My suitcase is so organized, I can simply pick out a cube that contains whatever I need. Love them!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: After all the hype I decided to purchase two different types of packing cubes and give them a try. I was excited about these due to the large size. I figured they’d be great for bulkier things. However, after the first use the seams split in multiple cubes and my clothes began coming out. I ended up shuffling items for the return trip, so I didn’t lose anything too valuable. You can see here my husbands swim trunks are attempting an escape from the bottom seam of the cube. I don’t recommend these. I purchased another brand to try and they were better so I ended up purchasing three additional sets - one for each member of the family, so we could each have our own color. The idea of cube packing did live up to the hype, just not with these cubes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 23, 2022
reviews.reviewText: I’ve been using packing cubes for almost 5 years and makes packing/unpacking so easy, I love how organized my luggage is with them, but this particular ones are very defective, since it was folded I didn’t notice one of them was ripped or not sewn together until I was closing it, had to move everything to another cube, size is good but I’m not sure if they will last long.
